172 A.3d 1082 IN THE MATTER OF WILLIAM R. HENDRICKSON, JR., DEPARTMENT OF COMMUNITY AFFAIRS. (WILLIAM R. HENDRICKSON, JR.—PETITIONER)

C-270 September Term 2017

079885 November 9, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003675-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
